This project MUST follow strict MVVM architecture with Riverpod.
- OOP (Object-Oriented Programming)
- KISS (Keep It Simple, Stupid)
- MVVM

Always put:
- data classes → models/
- data access → repositories/
- state & logic → providers/ (use Notifier / AsyncNotifier)
- UI → screens/ + widgets/

Feature-first structure: features/<feature>/providers | screens | widgets | models | repositories

Use ConsumerWidget / HookConsumerWidget for screens.
Never use setState or ChangeNotifier in new code.
Prefer riverpod_generator when possible.
Follow clean naming: business_card_detail_notifier.dart, not bloc/cubit.

When in doubt → read docs/architecture.md and docs/ai-instructions.md

See docs/ai-instructions.md for important rules (localization, etc).
